# Sub-B: Call chain: square(6) usa Call mul(6,6) -> 36. Verifica Call dentro F.
D 0 0 result Integer 0
D 0 0 prod Integer 0

F 0 0 mul [a, b]
R 0 0 Mul [a, b] prod
R 0 0 Ret [prod]
R 0 0 EndF

F 0 0 square [n]
R 0 0 Call [mul, n, n] sq
R 0 0 Ret [sq]
R 0 0 EndF

R 0 0 Call [square, 6] result
R 0 0 ExitTop [result]
